President Muhammadu Buhari has approved the immediate redeployment of two Ministers of State This was contained in a statement Tuesday evening by Willie Bassey, Director Information, Office of Secretary to the Government of the Federation. “Mr. Festus Keyamo, Minister of State for Niger Delta Affairs is to move to Ministry of Labour and Employment as Minister of State,” it read. “Senator Tayo Alasoadura is to move to Ministry of Niger Delta Affairs as Minister of State” “This redeployment takes effect from today, Tuesday 24th September, 2019.” Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.